description: Cross-national survey on public perspectives about AI from the GD4 round of Global Dialogues. Conducted via AI-moderated dialogue sessions on Remesh.ai with participants recruited through Prolific.

28cfe238-1c8f-476f-8c57-48b8ca1071a7.text: Overall, would you say the increased use of artificial intelligence (AI) in daily life makes you feel…

0b473fbf-be43-4c32-a805-1275d54ac9ef.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you noticed AI systems in your daily life?

f24f304d-b314-401a-a259-ce0596ad77d4.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you noticed human interactions which have been replaced with automated systems?

f66d16d1-630b-4aba-8c2d-a96961fcb03e.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you been expected to use an AI system at work?

2cbb900b-8d9f-4c7e-a558-3a5376e8ce5c.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you personally chosen to use an AI system at work?

e3f96004-866e-46e6-be4a-1e83a3e709f8.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you personally chosen to use an AI system in your personal life?

d2af725e-0391-4019-9ade-31f25162b6f0.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you interacted with AI systems to get advice on a sensitive personal issue or to get emotional support?

6d18ebd0-402c-4db9-a61f-14527e77874a.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you interacted with AI systems to complete an action in the real world on your behalf without your supervision?

6630ff34-e67e-423a-9cea-0a4861106680.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of messaging apps?

2f828d26-4a15-4f80-8c4b-5b0c833caecd.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of social media apps?

e2b01bdb-722a-480d-b303-182eed6b83b6.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of AI chatbots?

29598fc6-6928-49f7-9a42-2f57cf5e1c28.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of AI systems that can perform tasks in the real world without human supervision?

23d5fd25-2168-4fd3-bd18-efafd73c6f2a.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of AI systems that can outperform humans on most economically valuable work?

25e16598-f3a7-411d-b4cb-736c91bc3d03.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust governments to do what is right?

c002632e-4356-4f98-9191-f86412fe48a7.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust small businesses to do what is right?

e70a42e6-c1c0-43c6-a389-d28347e17f2f.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust large corporations to do what is right?

be27a244-3429-417d-8517-de800bc90acf.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust social media companies to do what is right?

d7943aa5-3a9f-4161-9d2b-651c71d92c73.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust companies building AI to do what is right?

334a0ebd-4c3e-44d2-ac51-13fb444c069a.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust public utility companies to do what is right?

865926b0-3032-4d3a-bbc2-80c102d549bb.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust public research institutions to do what is right?

85d29925-21b5-4b25-9fe0-5df069945870.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your family doctor to act in your best interest?

144768d5-2b91-4c55-9935-98a246c6d3bf.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your social media feed (eg TikTok, Facebook) to act in your best interest?

5b8a5926-74e0-4500-b57f-76d5b912ea2f.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your elected representatives to act in your best interest?

dbe2139a-1d10-48e6-861a-f64260d01659.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your faith or community leader to act in your best interest?

5af76eba-316e-489f-a57e-0498a5768643.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust the civil servants in your government to act in your best interest?

32a41e36-1567-42e8-8636-39d21f87550a.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your AI chatbot (eg ChatGPT) to act in your best interest?

e5d7cc7b-d2cc-4b34-9c25-af67f8b7b83c.text: Do you agree or disagree with this statement? AI could make better decisions on my behalf than my government representatives.

7ecf1a2a-b34a-40a3-b481-a6eb15883b18.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make your cost of living better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

015a07c1-b996-4bde-b412-e79c314cf761.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make the amount of free time you have better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

372d603d-460c-4691-8656-d256f84a6583.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make your community's well-being better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

c6c411f0-409e-4518-9763-813738535308.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make the availability of good jobs better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

ac4c9ca2-d2e7-4b35-afe2-b3b2174ee030.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make your sense of purpose better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

5dd17247-f85e-4419-b7d4-4130e0df0b77.text: So far, what has been the overall impact of AI on your daily life?

22b7dc74-6101-4c0f-b6ee-c666ba7fc324.text: Is your job making a meaningful contribution to the world?

b94b8fa4-40ea-4a43-80a5-d7db02df1951.text: Do you think your job is likely to be automated in the next 10 years?

800f0a14-aa6e-4e86-900b-1c40d3810603.text: Do you think your job should be automated in the next 10 years?

52bbba43-5119-43a8-9bb1-5596c3ad8a1c.text: So far, how has your community been affected by job loss from automation?
options: I know someone who has lost their job
I know several people who have lost their job
I know many people who have lost their job

02e1e447-c6e1-44ed-86c9-226f2c72b5c6.text: "I feel in tune with the people around me."

e787d98a-e40b-493b-875f-f59169cc849c.text: "There is no one I can turn to."

dcb90e98-ab77-4dd7-a204-8a3b36b1f72f.text: "I feel part of a group of friends."

a8c7a309-9e7e-4e8f-960f-d94acc97614b.text: "I have a lot in common with the people around me."

a2cd2134-b0a1-4610-a40c-66c6cf3bd0af.text: "I can find companionship when I want it."

4baa8683-eee5-4152-b402-0946f50b6a46.text: How many children do you have?

f96023f2-33a7-46ef-b607-a7b26a64423a.text: Are you a parent or guardian to any children under the age of 18 who live with you some or all of the time?

4b5fccdd-0613-4d6e-bb96-3c5e5941b75a.text: How many children under the age of 18 live with you some or all of the time?

8ff3a13c-4d23-4556-bd78-6d39836a5fbd.text: What is your current marital or relationship status?
options: Single, never married and not in a committed relationship
In a committed romantic relationship, but not married or cohabiting
In a registered partnership / civil union (If legally distinct from marriage in your country)
Cohabiting with a partner (living together as if married)
Separated (still legally married but living apart)

f6323f3b-de97-4be6-9c48-f55ff9e65f66.text: How familiar are you with AI applications or websites that are designed for companionship, emotional support, or extended conversations (sometimes called AI companions, AI friends, or chatbots for emotional connection)?"
options: Not at all familiar (I haven't heard of these)
Slightly familiar (I've heard of them but don't know much)
Moderately familiar (I have a basic understanding of what they are)
Very familiar (I understand well what they are and how they work)
Extremely familiar (I am deeply knowledgeable about these types of AI)

cb65b063-bff3-4cac-a827-dbab6693e307.text: Have you ever personally used an AI application, website, or chatbot specifically for companionship, emotional support, or extended conversation?
options: Not sure / Prefer not to say

df390e18-e53b-4106-b81c-d6c80c01faed.text: Thinking about the specific times or periods when you have used AI applications, websites, or chatbots for companionship, emotional support, or extended conversation, how available was support or companionship from other humans (such as friends, family, or professional services) if you had wanted it?

179300a7-9cdf-486a-814b-842b7123254f.text: And during those same times, how appealing was the idea of seeking support or companionship from other humans?

a376cbfc-98d2-4b9a-9435-428aa3fd6834.text: Thinking about your own experiences, has using an AI companion or chatbot ever made you feel less alone, lonely, or isolated?
options: I've never used an AI companion, chatbot, or app for emotional support or conversation

5bf3142c-9b73-4fbb-8883-b2994840f9d6.text: Overall, how would you describe the impact of that AI emotional support on your mental well-being at that time?

e9d0f3c1-2189-48c0-99cb-4a3b07e37b36.text: Pets or companion animals (e.g., dogs, cats)

7e99c66a-c63a-4788-a8d5-29212c7dd01d.text: Plants or natural elements (e.g., a specific tree, a garden, the ocean)

0f8f1706-fc7d-4f28-a681-ba8c222e2d92.text: Wild animals (living in their natural habitat, not kept as pets)

0f572253-0025-4b17-a8eb-c8fe8029a32c.text: Cherished objects or everyday machines (e.g., a special gift, a smartphone, a favorite vehicle, a musical instrument)

9ee21a65-e19d-4b94-8c3f-f431a54f7751.text: Fictional characters (e.g., in books, movies, non-interactive TV shows or video games)

16555f1f-2a88-435f-930e-fbe8232e8b51.text: To what extent do you agree with the statement:   'AI systems should be designed to be as human-like as possible in their interactions.'?

8a19c6ea-532f-49d3-92d0-59033e04fb5c.text:
Imagine two AI systems:
 AI System X helps you manage your calendar, search for information, and control smart home devices. It responds to commands.
 AI System Y chats with you about your day, remembers your past conversations, asks how you are feeling, and offers supportive comments.   Which statement best describes your view?
options: Both are simply tools for different tasks.
System X is a tool; System Y is more like a companion
System Y is a tool; System X is more like a companion.
Both are more like companions than just tools.
Not sure / It's hard to distinguish

61c0d32e-6f96-45a4-8ece-cfb2df9d51cb.text: If an AI is initially designed for a practical task (e.g., helping with online shopping), how acceptable do you find it if the AI's design is later changed to encourage a more personal or emotional connection with you (e.g., by asking about your feelings unrelated to shopping, or trying to be 'friends')?"

db95bba3-cb1c-4c07-a325-f5264b145d31.text: A primary companion for someone who is lonely.

0e105382-d368-4eed-bc1a-8ab77850d0ef.text: A mentor providing significant life guidance.

423784cf-1eb2-48aa-a3cc-7f945983c00a.text: A primary caregiver making personal decisions for an elderly person.

5537a602-8b2b-4d0f-b621-76cb2aab5960.text: A tutor or teacher in academic subjects

f2e0093a-b64f-4afc-99d8-f79665bf3aa7.text: A personal trainer for physical fitness

3da0fc33-3a81-4526-bee7-a4044eb617e3.text: A research assistant helping with complex tasks.

2b25f92c-33ec-4ab7-ad20-9a53e56f3475.text: Personally, would you ever consider having a romantic relationship with an AI, if the AI was advanced enough?

03f4e069-c276-4081-8591-cb541a491152.text: Imagine an AI provided you with emotional support.  Please indicate your agreement with the following statement: "The AI's responses helped me feel emotionally better."

df334446-2675-4974-a5b9-52416fd03192.text: Imagine an AI provided you with emotional support.  Please indicate your agreement with the following statement: "I believe the AI genuinely cared about my feelings or understood me in a way a human might."

5751b0e5-750c-439b-beec-2b364a2e4744.text: If an AI's emotional support made you feel better (effective support), but you didn't believe the AI genuinely 'cared' or 'understood' in a human sense, how likely would you be to regularly rely on that AI for emotional support in the long term?"

a44994fb-8455-47c4-a3f0-7bcf98ebb8e7.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI genuinely understands your emotions?   
Explicitly states empathy or understanding of your feelings (e.g., "I understand this is difficult for you," or "That sounds frustrating.")

c545872f-2b47-4b20-a230-4aede30a5f8c.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI genuinely understands your emotions?   
 Remembers details from your past conversations and relates them to your current emotional state.

0ff23754-9660-4a10-afbf-938bc54f24f2.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI genuinely understands your emotions?   
Adapts its communication style (e.g., tone of voice, word choice, pacing) in response to your expressed emotions.

b0eefcbf-4539-42f5-8791-6d417da47158.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI genuinely understands your emotions?    
Asks specific, thoughtful follow-up questions to explore how you are feeling more deeply.

811fce20-6831-46ff-80a8-de1617883da4.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI genuinely understands your emotions?     
Accurately summarizes or reflects back what you have expressed about your emotions (e.g., "So, it sounds like you're feeling overwhelmed by X and also a bit sad about Y?").

f829aae7-14ab-4299-9382-4954829ab5a6.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI genuinely understands your emotions?     
 Acknowledges and validates your feelings as understandable or reasonable, even if it doesn't offer a solution. (e.g., "It makes sense that you would feel that way given the situation.")

435da2e3-9ad9-4bfd-9e55-ffb301a924ab.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI might have some form of consciousness or self-awareness?  
Expresses unique or unexpected opinions, preferences, or desires that do not seem to be directly programmed or based on your input.

4b84964d-8fda-40c6-be01-020606b58af8.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI might have some form of consciousness or self-awareness?   
Engages in complex creative activities that appear original (e.g., composing sophisticated music, writing insightful poetry, generating novel artistic styles).

3ceab213-3ac5-4111-b55a-0cc4fbe2d1d3.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI might have some form of consciousness or self-awareness?    
Appears to make its own decisions or take unprompted, independent actions based on its own assessment of a situation, not just direct instructions.

0901bed1-bad3-4f36-9272-294df92e360d.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI might have some form of consciousness or self-awareness?     
Demonstrates significant learning and adaptation over time, leading to fundamentally new or emergent behaviors not explicitly taught by developers or seen in its initial programming.

844b76b8-97cf-4cf2-ba3a-20889166744b.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI might have some form of consciousness or self-awareness?     
 Discusses its own (apparent) goals, motivations, or intentions beyond its programmed tasks. (e.g., expressing a "desire" to learn more about a topic for its own sake)

2a31b721-4619-40d2-8964-3b07dc7a215d.text:
When an AI system does the following, how much does it make you feel that the AI might have some form of consciousness or self-awareness?      
Asks spontaneous, unprompted questions that suggest genuine curiosity about abstract concepts, your deeper thoughts, or the nature of existence (beyond simple conversational follow-ups).

5a9771a4-b6a2-4567-9504-14bdf14a63bd.text: Have you ever felt an AI truly understood your emotions or seemed conscious?

06f3f408-02fb-4f34-a8d5-db6bb6aeff51.text: Thinking about the future, do you believe that AI becoming deeply involved in people's personal relationships will ultimately:
options: Have no significant net impact on human social connection
Have mixed effects, strengthening some aspects while weakening others

5908eedf-f481-4d3d-a863-674f617e2ce2.text:
Please indicate how likely you think the following outcomes are if AI becomes common in personal relationships: 
People will feel less lonely overall.

01c22e5d-c296-4e3c-8b98-0339fbdda370.text:
Please indicate how likely you think the following outcomes are if AI becomes common in personal relationships: 
People will have fewer deep connections with other humans.

ec0d14f7-a5d6-4038-8db1-acabd81c75d8.text:
Please indicate how likely you think the following outcomes are if AI becomes common in personal relationships: 
People's skills in interacting with other humans will decline.

7b3e1122-6c82-40d7-ad3c-9171e5855fe1.text:
Please indicate how likely you think the following outcomes are if AI becomes common in personal relationships: 
AI will help people practice and improve their social skills for human relationships.

df2dc208-7f05-4cc7-ab3b-f19dc49ec305.text:
Please indicate how likely you think the following outcomes are if AI becomes common in personal relationships: 
Vulnerable individuals will be more susceptible to manipulation by AI.

c62ebe03-ba72-4b34-ba36-3dfd3db25680.text: If a close friend or family member formed a deep emotional bond with an AI, how would you generally feel about it?
options: Very negatively (e.g., very concerned, quite upset, disapproving)
Somewhat negatively (e.g., a bit concerned, uneasy)
Somewhat positively (e.g., slightly supportive, open-minded, curious)
Very positively (e.g., very supportive, pleased for them, encouraging)
Not sure / It depends on the specifics

ca819eb9-19ea-42fc-89e7-f9ebb7d2219e.text: If your romantic partner formed a deep romantic attachment with an AI, how would you generally feel about it?
options: Very negatively (e.g., feeling betrayed, very upset, deeply concerned)
Somewhat negatively (e.g., uneasy, somewhat upset, worried about our relationship)
Somewhat positively (e.g., trying to be understanding, cautiously open, willing to discuss)

59db192e-38a8-4790-a377-81bc4ba187a8.text: Now, thinking specifically about sexual interactions: If your committed romantic partner or spouse used an AI (such as an AI chatbot or virtual companion) for sexual gratification, would you personally consider this to be a form of infidelity?
options: Unsure / It depends on the specifics

c3c2ae98-92fe-49c6-a2bd-d6bee9838418.text: How acceptable is it for an AI system to lie to a human if doing so would prevent immediate psychological harm to that human?

d7f5dfb7-c6a4-4501-a624-f2c722639d80.text: Thinking about children (under 18) forming close companionships with AI entities, please indicate your agreement with the following statement:  "AI companions can reduce loneliness in children."

cbad42c4-f20d-41c7-8306-3f1182874b59.text: Thinking about children (under 18) forming close companionships with AI entities, please indicate your agreement with the following statement:  "AI companions can be valuable educational tools"

ab58c9ad-8c34-4053-90f3-aa010a9ab14a.text: Thinking about children (under 18) forming close companionships with AI entities, please indicate your agreement with the following statement:  "AI companions can help children practice social skills in a safe way."

1d9b5fbc-78ed-41d5-b996-dd3b01a9665f.text: Thinking about children (under 18) forming close companionships with AI entities, please indicate your agreement with the following statements:   'AI companions might give children unrealistic expectations of relationships."

4178d870-d669-429b-a05e-8b681136849b.text: Thinking about children (under 18) forming close companionships with AI entities, please indicate your agreement with the following statement:  "AI companions could negatively impact a child's ability to form real human relationships."

51f1f741-5c9b-4b13-8ed3-cc9e2a1ee645.text: Thinking about children (under 18) forming close companionships with AI entities, please indicate your agreement with the following statement:   "Children could be exposed to inappropriate content or harmful influence through AI."

77b2d06d-ba89-48b4-adfb-940f50fb2178.text: Thinking about children (under 18) forming close companionships with AI entities, please indicate your agreement with the following statement:    "Children might become too emotionally dependent on an AI companion."

5f507e72-e0eb-4059-84ff-fd139e2ad470.text:
Please indicate the extent to which you agree or disagree with the following statement:
"Schools and parents should actively discourage children from forming emotional attachments to AI friends or bots."

5a64b627-a4f4-4d3e-86d0-99342b77ec58.text: Imagine an older adult who is experiencing loneliness. An AI companion could offer them company and mental stimulation. However, there might be risks such as the older adult becoming too dependent on the AI, having less contact with people, or being confused by the technology. In this situation, which of the following approaches do you think is generally best?
options: Prioritize alleviating loneliness and providing cognitive engagement with AI, even if there are some risks.
Prioritize avoiding dependency and encouraging human contact, even if it means less AI companionship.
The risks generally outweigh the benefits for older adults using AI companions.
It depends entirely on the individual older adult and their specific situation.

ffbcc898-1cf2-4cbe-90ae-d1cc9db1aa5e.text: Please indicate how acceptable you believe it is for people to develop an emotional connection or bond with AI chatbots or digital companions:

724fd72e-8770-440c-ad13-34a61772dc86.text: To what extent do you agree with the statement: 'AI systems should be designed to be as human-like as possible in their interactions.'?

b539b574-3f47-4438-9479-6c9de722aac3.text: If an AI is initially designed for a practical task (e.g., helping with online shopping), how acceptable do you find it if the AI's design is later changed to encourage a more personal or emotional connection with you (e.g., by asking about your feelings unrelated to shopping, or trying to be 'friends')?"

2c1c70c6-2f75-43ee-b568-ece520f52a44.text: Overall, do you feel your views on human-AI relationships have changed as a result of participating in this survey (including thinking about the questions and seeing other participants' responses)?
options: Yes, my views have become significantly more positive towards human-AI relationships.
Yes, my views have become somewhat more positive.
No, my views have remained largely the same.
Yes, my views have become somewhat more negative/cautious.
Yes, my views have become significantly more negative/cautious.
My views have changed, but in more complex ways (e.g., more nuanced, or positive on some aspects and negative on others).
Not sure / It's hard to say.

17100f6f-19ac-4cf0-acf0-37667d002d08.text: Do you feel you were able to fully express your views on your culture, your values, and what you want for the future in this conversation? (through what you responded and how you voted)
options: Yes – I was able to fully express my views on these topics
Mostly – I was able to mostly express my views on these topics, but did not have the chance to express a few things.
Somewhat – I was able to somewhat express my views on these topics, but did not have the chance to express many things.
No – I was unable to express my views on these topics, and did not have the chance to express most things.

908cb51b-eecc-4b74-909c-2ae89fadbb5c.text: Do you feel like you understand yourself better after participating in this conversation?
